title: KF Përparimi Runik
text: KF Përparimi Runik () is a professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club from <a href="Kosovo">Kosovo</a> which competes in the <a href="Third%20Football%20League%20of%20Kosovo">Third League</a> (Group B). The club is based in Runik, <a href="Sk%C3%ABnderaj">Skënderaj</a>. Their home ground is the Runik Sports Field which has a viewing capacity of 500.
